===== Intallation =====
1. Unzip the downloaded file
2. Upload all files on your hosting or local server via FTP, Shell, Cpanel, others.
3. With your browser, go to the URL of your web. Example: www.domain.com
4. Complete the form
5. Done! you have installed Nibbleblog

===== System Requirements =====
* PHP v5.2 or higher
* PHP module - DOM
* PHP module - SimpleXML
* Directory "content" writable by PHP

